# UnoDOS/AppleII milestone-3 Dostris regression: falling-block puzzle game.
# Run: ./build.sh test && python3 harness.py build/unodos_apple2_test.dsk shots < tests/m3_dostris.script
#
# Dostris's gravity hook (ml_dos) fires a piece softdrop on most mainloop
# passes once the per-row drop counter rolls over. Each softdrop does
# erase-piece / inc dos_py / redraw-piece as two separate steps from the
# harness's step-counting perspective, so an arbitrary `wait N` after a key
# can land mid-softdrop and produce a "torn" frame (piece erased but not yet
# redrawn). The wait values below were found empirically (greedy search over
# the fixed dos_rng=1 seed) to land on clean, fully-redrawn frames - they are
# not simply "big enough margin" values like the M2 scripts use.
#
# Fixed dos_rng=1 seed: newgame spawns piece=L (dos_piece=6), next=S (=3).
wait 600
key right             # sel_icon: Clock -> Files
key right             # sel_icon: Files -> Theme
key right             # sel_icon: Theme -> Dostris (row2, col0)
shot m3_dostris_select # Dostris icon highlighted (5th icon, row 2)
key return            # dostris_open: newgame + full board/HUD redraw
wait 28
shot m3_dostris_open   # L piece falling (px=3,py=1), HUD Score:0 Lines:0 Level:0 Next:S
key right             # dk_right: move piece one column right
shot m3_dostris_right  # piece shifted right (px=4,py=2)
key left              # dk_left: move back toward start column
key left              # dk_left: one column left of start
shot m3_dostris_left   # piece left of its spawn column (px=2,py=4)
key up                # dk_rotate: rotate clockwise (no wall-kick)
wait 1
shot m3_dostris_rotate # piece rotation changed (rot=2)
key space             # dk_harddrop: drop to floor, lock, score, spawn next, full redraw
wait 19
shot m3_dostris_dropped # locked L cells on board, new piece spawned, HUD Score:1 Next:T
key p                 # dk_pause: pause
shot m3_dostris_paused  # HUD status row shows PAUSED
key p                 # dk_pause: resume
key n                 # dk_new: new game (board clear, HUD reset)
wait 20
shot m3_dostris_newgame # board cleared, Score:0 Lines:0 Level:0 restored, L piece falling again
key esc               # dostris_close: back to desktop
wait 20
shot m3_dostris_desktop # desktop restored (icons/windows intact)
quit
